{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"g3c4d5e6f7a8","type":"group","x":-200,"y":-700,"width":1760,"height":1600,"color":"6","label":"后端/Agent 架构流程"},
		{"id":"g2b3c4d5e6f7","type":"group","x":-1080,"y":-700,"width":830,"height":2060,"color":"4","label":"前端对话流程"},
		{"id":"g1a2b3c4d5e6","type":"group","x":-1080,"y":-920,"width":2900,"height":50,"color":"5","label":"图例：绿=用户操作 青=输入处理 紫=AI 处理 红=数据 黄=路由 橙=交互"},
		{"id":"u1a2b3c4d5e6","type":"text","text":"U1. 用户点击浮动按钮","x":-1060,"y":-690,"width":240,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"u2b3c4d5e6f7","type":"text","text":"U2. ChatWidget 面板打开\n显示欢迎页或历史消息","x":-1060,"y":-550,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"u3c4d5e6f7a8","type":"text","text":"U3. 用户输入文字\n或粘贴/上传图片","x":-1060,"y":-350,"width":240,"height":100,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"i1d5e6f7a8b9","type":"text","text":"I1. 有图片时：OCR 检测\nImagePreview 显示 loading","x":-730,"y":-570,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"i2e6f7a8b9c0","type":"text","text":"I2. OCR 识别中...\nImagePreview 持续 loading","x":-730,"y":-410,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"i3f7a8b9c0d1","type":"text","text":"I3. 识别完成\n文字合并到输入框","x":-720,"y":-220,"width":240,"height":80,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r1a8b9c0d1e2","type":"text","text":"R1. onSend() 路由\n三分支判断当前状态","x":-1060,"y":-10,"width":240,"height":100,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"r2b9c0d1e2f3","type":"text","text":"F7. editingField 模式\n用户输入直接替换字段值\n界面：AI 气泡显示『已更新字段』","x":-650,"y":-45,"width":280,"height":120,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"r3c0d1e2f3a4","type":"text","text":"F8. awaitingFollowUp 模式\n用户补充缺失字段\n合并后重新走正常流程","x":-730,"y":210,"width":280,"height":120,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"v1e2f3a4b5c6","type":"text","text":"V1. 用户气泡出现\n（右对齐，蓝色气泡）\n内容 + 可选图片","x":-910,"y":530,"width":260,"height":120,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"v3a4b5c6d7e8","type":"text","text":"V3. 思考中区域实时更新\n← onStep 回调推送\n显示当前步骤：\n『加载上下文...』→『LLM 意图识别...』→『工具执行...』","x":-970,"y":1000,"width":280,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"v4b5c6d7e8f9","type":"text","text":"V4. 思考中区域\n可点击展开查看推理链\n显示步骤详情：置信度/来源标注","x":-620,"y":1120,"width":280,"height":140,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"b10e1f2a3b4c","type":"text","text":"B10. LLM Function Calling\n百炼 API 直连\n返回 tool_calls + _source 标注","x":1130,"y":-330,"width":300,"height":180,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"b12a3b4c5d6e","type":"text","text":"B12. SQLite 数据库\nrecords / business_trip / chat_history / app_config","x":1130,"y":550,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"b13b4c5d6e7f","type":"text","text":"B13. ToolRegistry\nZod schema → JSON Schema\n20+ 工具注册","x":770,"y":30,"width":330,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"x7c1d2e3f4a5","type":"text","text":"X7. SQLite 持久化\nchat_history 保存消息\nrecords 保存记录\nlearning_data 保存修正","x":-190,"y":710,"width":260,"height":120,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"b15d6e7f8a9b","type":"text","text":"B15. ConfirmCard\n用户确认后 toolRegistry.execute\n写入 DB + 保存学习数据","x":820,"y":390,"width":280,"height":120,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"x1d6e7f8a9b0","type":"text","text":"X1. ConfirmCard 确认\n→ confirmRecord → 重复检测\n→ toolRegistry 执行\n→ 保存学习数据 → confirmed","x":360,"y":40,"width":260,"height":160,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"x6e3f4a5b6c7","type":"text","text":"X6. ToolResult\nrender: card/text/followUp\ndata: 结构化数据\nmessage: 用户可见文本","x":-80,"y":-10,"width":300,"height":140,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"b4e5f6a7b8c9","type":"text","text":"B4. AgentEngine.processMessage()\n三阶段：加载上下文 → LLM → 工具执行","x":-130,"y":-630,"width":280,"height":180,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"b8c9d0e1f2a3","type":"text","text":"B8. LLM 意图识别 ← 耗时最长\n调用 callLLMWithTools\n解析 tool_calls","x":770,"y":-560,"width":260,"height":120,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"b9d0e1f2a3b4","type":"text","text":"B9. 工具执行\n路由到 ToolRegistry\n返回 ToolResult + steps","x":770,"y":-250,"width":260,"height":120,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"b11f2a3b4c5d","type":"text","text":"B11. Rust 后端\ncall_llm / SQLite CRUD","x":1200,"y":-40,"width":300,"height":170,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"r4d1e2f3a4b5","type":"text","text":"F9. 正常流程\n调用 chat.sendMessage()","x":-1060,"y":300,"width":240,"height":100,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"v2f3a4b5c6d7","type":"text","text":"V2. AI 气泡出现\n（左对齐，灰色气泡）\n显示『思考中...』spinner","x":-1040,"y":750,"width":260,"height":120,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"x2e7f8a9b0c1","type":"text","text":"X2. 取消\n→ cancelRecord\n→ status=cancelled\n→ 内容=『请重新输入』","x":220,"y":590,"width":260,"height":120,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"x3f8a9b0c1d2","type":"text","text":"X3. 编辑字段\n→ FollowUpCard 选择字段\n→ startEditField → 用户输入\n→ 触发 editingField 模式","x":-130,"y":200,"width":260,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"x4a9b0c1d2e3","type":"text","text":"X4. FollowUpCard\n→ 选择缺失字段\n→ 用户补充输入\n→ 触发 awaitingFollowUp 模式","x":100,"y":390,"width":260,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b6a7b8c9d0e1","type":"text","text":"B6. 构建 SystemMessage\n拼接 prompt + 偏好 + 学习上下文","x":290,"y":-360,"width":330,"height":110,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"b5f6a7b8c9d0","type":"text","text":"B5. 加载上下文\n并行读取 dispatch prompt / 偏好 / 学习数据","x":270,"y":-550,"width":350,"height":90,"color":"6"}
	],
